{"tid":1747511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭定康反駁法工委 促外相介入","createTime":"2019-11-23T08:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T10:28:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9cee0e4a899ed8d0a694b5a125ecbfe95969c71c","tid":1747511,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:59:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191123/ISBYMH5P5K6QWOU73QND6GX5YU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191123%2FISBYMH5P5K6QWOU73QND6GX5YU%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpKooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=abeeaf3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191123%2FISBYMH5P5K6QWOU73QND6GX5YU%2F&h=b6b9b34f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191123/ISBYMH5P5K6QWOU73QND6GX5YU/</a><br />\n<br />\n彭定康反駁法工委 促外相介入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會法制工作委員會發言人，早前批評香港高等法院裁定蒙面法違憲，稱只有全國人大常委會才能判斷法律是否違反《基本法》。末代港督彭定康（Chris Patten）前日致函現任英國外相藍韜文（Dominic Raab），斥全國人大嚴重損害香港法治，要求外交部介入。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康在信中寫道，全國人大聲明完全違反《中英聯合聲明》第三章第三條，列明香港特區擁有獨立的司法權，包括最終裁決權，令人極為關注，更指「如果全國人大繼續否決香港法院的判決，全國人大的聲明將嚴重損害司法獨立及香港的法治&hellip;&hellip;亦大大削弱在一國兩制原則下承諾予香港的高度自治。如果香港法治及自治受到威脅，香港作為全球最重要國際金融和貿易中心的成功將受到威脅」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n彭定康要求藍韜文採取行動，就此事盡快發表強烈的公開聲明，並考慮就北京違反《中英聯合聲明》會採取甚麼行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191123/large/1574440838_cf4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191123%2Flarge%2F1574440838_cf4a.jpg&h=f38b2b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彭定康致英國外相的信中指全國人大聲明完全違反《中英聯合聲明》。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英議員促履行對港責任<br />\n<br />\n另外，英國下月舉行大選，在野自由民主黨（自民黨）黨魁斯溫森（Jo Swinson）在大選政綱的對外政策中，承諾重新開啟英國國民（海外）護照（簡稱BNO）的申請，並賦予所有BNO持有人居英權，稱是「履行英國對港人的法律和道德責任」。<br />\n<br />\n倫敦和威斯敏斯特市選區的自民黨參選議員烏穆納（Chuka Umunna）在英國《獨立報》也撰文指出，香港警方及政府暴力鎮壓示威者，明確顯示中國拒絕遵守《中英聯合聲明》的承諾，又指「至今為止，英國政府對局勢視而不見，未有表現出任何領導才能或採取果斷行動，不可原諒」。烏穆納稱維護民主、人權和法治將是自民黨的核心，會採取切實行動履行英國對香港的承諾和義務。<br />\n<br />\n英國《衞報》/香港監察"},{"pid":"e3cac088c27abbe39937d26cb503e6355c7dceb9","tid":1747511,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:09:57.000Z","msg":"肥彭可能唔知英撚已經奶哂共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a7e2199ff326a56e741c815cc3111c93141ce2","tid":1747511,"uid":37528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:11:35.000Z","msg":"肥彭應該好難過，佢都算係親手將香港交俾班野蠻人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ccc66082825e87b3c092073bd99aa752f34147","tid":1747511,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"彭督👍"},{"pid":"fb4ed10641b7ab5905fc469a34a405c2590d393c","tid":1747511,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:28:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>"},{"pid":"8582a6595a05ecfff5e467299d38ca092151e91b","tid":1747511,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:28:14.000Z","msg":"快D回歸英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9737248427e5624d3827649f9f0735e0a0ff2e4e","tid":1747511,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"Real Sir"},{"pid":"369c6dd21363058f86503beaffafdb9f48353d8f","tid":1747511,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9737248427e5624d3827649f9f0735e0a0ff2e4e","tid":1747511,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"Real Sir"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:35:13.000Z","msg":"Lord 呀"},{"pid":"1da6fa911ac7ad7f4a5ca8b1ad26d1723db27372","tid":1747511,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:36:24.000Z","msg":"肥彭返嚟香港啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e0aa8b4c9f95d248ffce5185537812130a33dc","tid":1747511,"uid":120064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:37:36.000Z","msg":"對比之下，衛奕信真係唔撚想理香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405b173dab0791fdd4463f6029cdf9551d190345","tid":1747511,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"369c6dd21363058f86503beaffafdb9f48353d8f","tid":1747511,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9737248427e5624d3827649f9f0735e0a0ff2e4e","tid":1747511,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"Real Sir"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:35:13.000Z","msg":"Lord 呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}